txt.en: 'Good to see you, [placeholder]. Our scouts have discovered an Ekhamâti camp in Khûd Zagin and they appear to have an abundance of gold stored there. I ask that you travel to the camp and take as much gold as you can find so we can put it to better use supplying Mizâdi's forces.\n\n'There have also been reports of brutal dôla in the camp by the names of Omurtóko, Khisónto, and Purombóro. I ask that you put an end to them while you are there.'
Your mission is to travel to the Ekhamâti camp, defeat the dôla and rob them of their gold in order to supply Mizâdi's forces.
There is no twist in this mission.

'I am glad for your return, [placeholder]. This gold will do so much good in helping Mizâdi! I thank you! And putting a stop to those dôla will also be great news for our soldiers who have heard the stories of their cruelty.'
